responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "0E8BB6C64F574B0D23B51A8C61E3C6AB", "The Riverlands belong to the Ashen Flame - by right of conquest, godling. Your people were driven out in the Time of Tribulation, and we remained. As the Seasons turn, we find our camps beset at times by the feral goblins, and we drive them away. Since the return of the godkin though, the pests have become bolder, stronger. I ween they make pacts with the cult of the Sighted, and from new masters draw new strength. I, Tul, lead the scouting party here to find them out.")
name: SQ_34_Tul_34
